To {bankName}:

I am hereby revoking my prior opt-in consent for overdraft service on ATM withdrawals and one-time debit card transactions on my account ending in {lastFour}.

Under 12 CFR §1005.17, this revocation is effective as soon as reasonably practicable upon your receipt of this notice. Please decline any future ATM or one-time debit transactions that would overdraw the available balance, rather than paying them and charging an overdraft fee.

I do not consent to re-enrollment absent a fresh affirmative opt-in on my part.

Account holder: {userName}
Date: {today}

Sincerely,
{userName}
